snippet.title: Tiny Tina's Wonderlands - Release Date Announcement Trailer | Game Awards 2021
snippet.description:
Will Arnett voices introduces this trailer for Tiny Tina's Wonderland, the upcoming Borderlands spin-off starring its tiniest and fiercest DM, Tiny Tina herself. Releasing on March 25, 2022.

#IGN #GameAwards2021 #Gaming
